ame from Aquitaine in south-west France to be the wife of  King Henry II . It was also borne by Eleanor of Provence, the wife of  Henry III , and Eleanor of Castile, wife of  Edward I ."]}]}],"lifeSummary":"Ellen was born about 1292, in Beeston, Cheshire, England, United Kingdom. She married Lord Henry de Beeston in 1320, in Beeston, Cheshire, England, United Kingdom. They were the parents of at least 3 sons. She died about 1335, at the age of 45."},"et":{"about 1292–about 1335":"umbes 1292–umbes 1335","1290–1342":"1290–1342","1321–1362":"1321–1362","1325–1370":"1325–1370","1327–1395":"1327–1395","1292–1335":"1292–1335","about 1292":"umbes 1292","Abt 1325":"umbes 1325","1395":"1395","1362":"1362","1370":"1370","1292":"1292","1290":"1290","1327":"1327","1325":"1325","1335":"1335","1321":"1321","1320":"1320","1342":"1342","about 1335":"umbes 1335","about 1321":"umbes 1321","of Beeston, Cheshire, England":"Beeston, Cheshire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","Beeston,Cheshire,England":"Beeston, Cheshire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","Beeston, Cheshire, England":"Beeston, Cheshire, England"},"fi":{"about 1292–about 1335":"noin 1292–noin 1335","1290–1342":"1290–1342","1321–1362":"1321–1362","1325–1370":"1325–1370","1327–1395":"1327–1395","1292–1335":"1292–1335","about 1292":"noin 1292","Abt 1325":"noin 1325","1395":"1395","1362":"1362","1370":"1370","1292":"1292","1290":"1290","1327":"1327","1325":"1325","1335":"1335","1321":"1321","1320":"1320","1342":"1342","about 1335":"noin 1335","about 1321":"noin 1321","of Beeston, Cheshire, England":"Beeston, Cheshire, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","Beeston,Cheshire,England":"Beeston, Cheshire, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","Beeston, Cheshire, England":"Beeston, Cheshire, England"},"fr":{"about 1292–about 1335":"environ 1292–environ 1335","1290–1342":"1290–1342","1321–1362":"1321–1362","1325–1370":"1325–1370","1327–1395":"1327–1395","1292–1335":"1292–1335","about 1292":"environ 1292","Abt 1325":"environ 1325","1395":"1395","136